Flipper Zero
• Multi-purpose wireless and RFID testing device.
• Threat: Can analyze IoT and wireless communication vulnerabilities.
• Ethical Use: Used for testing smart device and embedded system security.

ATM Skimmer
• Device placed in ATM slots to capture card data.
• Threat: Used for financial fraud and identity theft.
• Ethical Use: Used to improve ATM physical and payment security systems.
